 {
  "text": "Hello, this is a short note about business emails. A good email has four parts. First, a clear subject line. Then a greeting, like Dear Maria. After that, the body with your message. Finally, a closing, like Best regards, and your signature. Keep it short and clear. If you have a file, attach it and say please find attached. Thank you.",
  "voice": "arthur",
  "file": "a5_listening1.mp3"
 },
 {
  "text": "Hi, this is Fernanda. I am writing a short message about my first email to a supplier. I start with the subject line. Then I write Dear Carlos as the greeting. In the body, I say I am writing to schedule a call about a coffee shipment. I close with Best regards and my signature. I also attach the contract. Please reply when you can. Thank you.",
  "voice": "ellen",
  "file": "a5_listening2.mp3"
 },
 {
